pageProduct.name: Aussie Bodies Protein Bar Lo Carb Crunchy Blueberry Almond 40g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

12g PROTEIN
1.9g SUGARS
HIGH FIBRE
No artificial colours or preservatives

Our Pro-active Nutrition products help your shape body from the inside out. Since 1991

Product Claims: With, DARK CHOCOLATE, BLUEBERRIES, ROASTED ALMONDS, CHIA SEEDS, 12g PROTEIN, 1.9g SUGARS, HIGH FIBRE, No artificial colours or preservatives

Size: 40g

Flavour: Blueberry Almond Crunch

Serving Size: 40g

Servings Per Pack: 1

KEY FEATURES

• Proactive Nutrition
• Great Tasting
• Guilt-Free Indulgence
• Source of Fibre
• Source of Protein

Warnings

"Contains: Milk, Soy, Cereals Containing Gluten (Wheat) and Tree Nuts (Almonds).
May Contain: Cereals Containing Gluten (Oats), Peanuts, Tree Nuts (Hazelnuts) and Sesame Seeds.
"

CAUTION

Excess consumption may have a laxative effect.

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Aussie Bodies® Protein Blend (35%) (Soy Protein Crisps (Soy Protein Isolate, Tapioca Starch, Salt), Whey Protein Concentrate (Milk), Milk Protein Concentrate), No Added Sugar Dark Chocolate (25%) (Cocoa Mass, Cocoa Butter, Sweeteners (Polydextrose, Erythritol, Steviol Glycosides), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Flavour), Sweeteners [Polydextrose, Maltitol (Wheat)], Dried Sweetened Blueberries (4.5%), Roasted Almonds (3%), Humectant (Glycerol), Vegetable Fat, Butter (Milk), Vegetable Gums (Acacia Gum, Xanthan Gum), Black Chia Seeds (1%), Flavours, Salt, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin).

Contains: Contains: Milk, Soy, Cereals Containing Gluten (Wheat) and Tree Nuts (Almonds).
May Contain: Cereals Containing Gluten (Oats), Peanuts, Tree Nuts (Hazelnuts) and Sesame Seeds.

Allergen Contains: Almonds| Milk| Soy| Tree Nuts| Wheat| Cereals Containing Gluten

Allergen May Be Present: Hazelnuts| Oats| Peanuts| Sesame Seeds| Tree Nuts| Cereals Containing Gluten

Directions

Store in a cool, dry place, below 30°C. Keep out of direct sunlight.
